booleanFormulaEntities

Class BooleanLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • booleanFormulaEntities.BooleanLiteral

  • public class BooleanLiteral
extends java.lang.Object
    defines any boolean literal in any boolean formula. input should be fixedOrderExpression since A > B is the same as B < A, this class is responsible for keeping a uniform way of expressing it as B < A , it is also responsible for keeping a fixed order of left and right hand side for expression like A = B and B = A
    Author:
    tingxie
